SUMMARY:Latino Founders Forum - Lymbar Hosted
DESCRIPTION:Register here: https://luma.com/Latino-Founders-Forum \nThe June edition of the Latino Founders Forum Houston is on June 30th ⚽🎉 \n​After a strong launch that brought out 50+ founders\, operators\, investors\, creatives\, and professionals\, the forum is keeping the momentum going with a special World Cup Celebration edition of our monthly gathering. \n​Yes\, it’s called Latino Founders Forum — but it’s not only for Latinos. Anyone is welcome to pull up\, grab a drink\, wear their favorite soccer jersey\, make meaningful connections\, and be part of the community. \n​This is a monthly event for people building real things in Houston. While the forum is rooted in supporting and elevating Latino founders\, the room is open to anyone who values entrepreneurship\, culture\, community\, and genuine relationships. \nThey’re back at The Lymbar inside the Ion for another high-quality happy hour designed to bring together founders\, funders\, advisors\, builders\, creatives\, and professionals who want to meet ambitious people in a room that actually feels worth being in. \n​This month\, they’re bringing a World Cup vibe to the night and inviting guests to wear their favorite soccer jersey as we celebrate culture\, connection\, and community in Houston. Expect a great atmosphere\, strong energy\, good drinks\, and the kind of conversations that make these events worth showing up for. \n​Come for the jerseys\, drinks\, and festive energy. Stay for the people\, the conversations\, and the chance to be part of Houston’s growing startup and business community. \n​If you came to one of the earlier events\, you already know the energy. If you haven’t yet\, this is a great one to start with. \n​Built by founders. Powered by community. Open to everyone.
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/latino-founders-forum-lymbar-hosted/
LOCATION:The Lymbar
CATEGORIES:3rd Party Registration
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://iondistrict.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/LLF-Social.png
